name: Cyber Sea Creatures - Megakane
description: Tiger shark once worshipped by indigenous tribes as a protector of the sea has now been turned into a monstrosity by an invading alien species. Megakane has undergone countless experiments and genetic mutations that have made him a force to be reckoned with. Plasma tail fin that can both slide and fire off plasma beams. Rhino plated skin for protection and titanium bladed side fins allow him to shred through even the toughest of foes. #Fear4Hen
